description: A very interesting guy today. Two things brought him into my office. He wanted to move to Prague and find a job with a nice career potential. And he actually looked like he might pull it off. I could tell he was quite smart and ambitious. His hobbies, sports and money, were particularly interesting to me. What a perfect combination. I offered him one of the best positions I had open. He very much liked the prospect of working at a bank. The fee wasn´t that steep for him but money saved is money gained so he accepted the alternative way of paying. I could see greed in his eyes, and maybe curiosity. I have no idea if he was at least a bit bi or not. What matters is that he sucked me in a way I will long remember. And he will not forget about our little meeting either. I´m sure about that.
title: Dirty Scout 59
